title: #140 - Theo Von & ME
description: Comedian Theo Von & I hang out in the Mancave & talk about our experience on Reality Bites Back, growing up poor in Louisiana w/ a 70 yearold father, getting emancipated at 14, getting attacked by cats, riding black kids to school on his bike, his time on Road Rules on MTV, and how his stand-up got so fucking good!
